Package at.tugraz.ist.ase.cacdr.algorithms.hs.labeler

Interface IHSLabelable

All Superinterfaces:
Cloneable
All Known Implementing Classes:
FastDiagV2Labeler, FastDiagV3Labeler, FlexDiagLabeler, QuickXPlainLabeler
public interface IHSLabelable extends Cloneable
Defines an interface for HS algorithms' theorem prover. In the "label" step, the HS-tree and HSDAG algorithms use a theorem prover to determine a conflict or a diagnosis.
Author:
David - source: https://github.com/jaccovs/Master-project, Viet-Man Le (vietman.le@ist.tugraz.at)
